      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANGO CANS (1) has placed at the last three runs, the latest finishing second (31.15) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. Has the inside draw and looks tough to beat. STATE OF MADNESS (3) in the money last time at this track (31.27) in a NG, finishing a 4 length third. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. PAW SHAYNA (2) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 30.99 beating MANGO CANS. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Sure to be thereabouts. EPIC STORY (7) is always hard to beat when he races at this trip.",
